# Beads exports its tracker to .beads/issues.jsonl. The line order is not
# stable across `bd` commands -- memory (_type:memory) records get reshuffled
# with no semantic change -- which otherwise shows up as permanent "dirty"
# git status churn. `bd export` has no sort/order flag today, so the reorder
# itself must be fixed upstream (see the tracked follow-up issue).
#
#   merge=union           avoid spurious merge conflicts on append-mostly JSONL
#   linguist-generated    collapse it in diff/review UIs (it is generated)
.beads/issues.jsonl merge=union linguist-generated=true
